text: Johanne Guillou is a Martiniquais footballer who plays as a defender for the Martinique women's national team. ==International career== Guillou capped for Martinique at senior level during the 2014 CONCACAF Women's Championship. == References == == External links == * Category:Living people Category:Martiniquais women's footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Martinique women's international footballers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
